description: Welcome to the newest condominium development in South Boston named Vesta! Coming to South Boston in 2024. Vesta is already 40% reserved! Amenities include common and private roof decks with Boston skyline views, a top floor clubroom w/ a wet bar, an outdoor pet play area and standard underground garage parking. Vesta will also be a professionally managed elevator building.  Residences will feature high end finishes including Carrara Quartz countertops and backsplashes, Metropolitan cabinetry, Bosch kitchen appliances including gas cooking, 'vented' in-unit washers and dryers and Kahrs Life Collection hardwood flooring.  Luxuriously appointed bathrooms will include Ultra White Quartz countertops, Residence 506 includes garage parking & private roof deck. Vesta will also include ground floor retail space, which will include Bell's Grocery Market and a local coffee shop. Bell's will offer daily conveniences such as groceries, prepared foods and wine/beer.
